    <item>
      <title>CrowdStrike 将 Epic IT 崩溃归咎于内容更新缺陷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/crowdstrike-blames-defect-in-content-update-for-epic-it-crash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[身处全球大规模 IT 中断事件中心的网络安全公司 CrowdStrike Holdings Inc. 表示，安全机制中的一个漏洞导致有缺陷的数据在一次拙劣的更新中发送给客户，从而导致了上周的崩溃。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/crowdstrike-blames-defect-in-content-update-for-epic-it-crash</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 07:52:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着重组的推进，Atos 董事长 Mustier 出任首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/atos-ceo-paul-saleh-departs-deal-with-creditors-moves-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的法国 IT 公司 Atos SE 在不到三年的时间内任命了第六位首席执行官，同时该集团正在推进其债权人的重组计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/atos-ceo-paul-saleh-departs-deal-with-creditors-moves-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 06:51:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国 Orange 抵制价格战，收入上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/orange-revenue-rises-in-french-market-after-resisting-price-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国最大的电话公司 Orange SA 报告称，在拒绝降价以与本土市场上更便宜的竞争对手竞争后，该公司收入出现增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/orange-revenue-rises-in-french-market-after-resisting-price-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 05:30:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>收费策略初见成效，裕信银行上调收入目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/unicredit-lifts-revenue-capital-goals-as-profit-tops-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于费用和贷款收入增加，意大利联合信贷银行第二季度利润超出分析师预期，该行上调了全年净收入目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/unicredit-lifts-revenue-capital-goals-as-profit-tops-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 05:03:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者等待人工智能带来回报，Alphabet 股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/alphabet-s-revenue-boosted-by-cloud-computing-search-ads</link>
      <description><![CDATA[谷歌母公司 Alphabet Inc. 股价在盘前交易中下跌，此前该公司投入了更多资源，以超越人工智能领域的竞争对手，支出高于分析师的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/alphabet-s-revenue-boosted-by-cloud-computing-search-ads</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 20:10:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德州仪器的前景缓解了人们对芯片行业衰退的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/texas-instruments-gives-in-line-forecast-calming-downturn-fear</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德州仪器公司 (Texas Instruments Inc.) 发布的销售前景表明库存过剩现象即将结束，这让投资者确信该公司芯片的主要市场正在复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/texas-instruments-gives-in-line-forecast-calming-downturn-fear</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 20:08:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Temenos 因业绩指引下调、Hindenburg 报告影响销售而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/temenos-cuts-guidance-as-hindenburg-report-weighs-on-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Temenos AG 公布第二季度营收低于分析师预期，随后下调了全年业绩预期，该公司将此归咎于做空机构 Hindenburg Research 报告的后遗症。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/temenos-cuts-guidance-as-hindenburg-report-weighs-on-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 16:26:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
